{"tid":939291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"部份南美洲難民要求收取五萬美金方自願回國 [sosad]","createTime":"2018-12-13T04:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T00:28:08.000Z","uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8734aac3cfe85a32eeb03bf1136d749bfb152697","tid":939291,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:03:57.000Z","msg":"真係有病 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n======================<br />\n&bull;Two groups of migrants wrote letters to the consulate, giving 72 hours to reply<br />\n&bull;One of the groups was made up of about 100 migrants, the other one of about 50<br />\n&bull;Their list of demands included speeding up the asylum application process<br />\n&bull;They also asked the US to remove Honduran President Hernandez from office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/10/7325740-6487193-image-m-45_1544612326256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F10%2F7325740-6487193-image-m-45_1544612326256.jpg&h=1a59e902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Migrants from Central America hold an El Salvador flag outside the US consulate in Tijuana, Mexico, asking American authorities to speed up the asylum application process<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/11/7325540-6487193-image-m-47_1544612421060.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F11%2F7325540-6487193-image-m-47_1544612421060.jpg&h=9a2914c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Two groups of migrants marched to the consulate with demands to the Trump administration<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/13/7330146-6487193-image-a-4_1544620244825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F13%2F7330146-6487193-image-a-4_1544620244825.jpg&h=6a9b9204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Members of the caravan are seen standing outside the US consulate in Tijuana, Mexico<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/20/7349242-6487193-image-a-8_1544648166944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F20%2F7349242-6487193-image-a-8_1544648166944.jpg&h=e703dc08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Migrants from Honduras, part of a caravan of thousands from Central America trying to reach the United States, walk next to the border fence in Tijuana, Mexico, December 12<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/20/7349264-6487193-image-a-12_1544648192578.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F20%2F7349264-6487193-image-a-12_1544648192578.jpg&h=afa9fd3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Migrants look on as their father walks through a sewage water tunnel to cross the border fence<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/20/7349276-6487193-image-m-4_1544648124927.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F20%2F7349276-6487193-image-m-4_1544648124927.jpg&h=2cddc343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A young child is seen being picked up and handed to a man straddling the border fence separate Mexico from the US Wednesday <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/20/7349274-6487193-image-a-5_1544648133566.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F20%2F7349274-6487193-image-a-5_1544648133566.jpg&h=3ce2cf5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Multiple Honduran nationals from the migrant caravan scaled the fence trying to reach California <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/20/7349252-6487193-image-a-10_1544648181881.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F20%2F7349252-6487193-image-a-10_1544648181881.jpg&h=936fa3ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/20/7349234-6487193-image-a-11_1544648181966.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F20%2F7349234-6487193-image-a-11_1544648181966.jpg&h=c417017b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/20/7349246-6487193-image-a-9_1544648171143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F20%2F7349246-6487193-image-a-9_1544648171143.jpg&h=8b26eb16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The migrants look at US Customs and Border Protection officials in San Diego County after crossing illegally from Mexico <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/13/7325744-6487193-They_are_part_of_a_caravan_of_thousand_migrants_from_Central_Ame-a-1_1544620759597.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F13%2F7325744-6487193-They_are_part_of_a_caravan_of_thousand_migrants_from_Central_Ame-a-1_1544620759597.jpg&h=de0031c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n They are part of a caravan of thousand migrants from Central America trying to enter the US<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/12/13/7325742-6487193-Among_the_demands_migrants_asked_the_US_to_accept_more_asylum_ap-a-2_1544620759811.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F13%2F7325742-6487193-Among_the_demands_migrants_asked_the_US_to_accept_more_asylum_ap-a-2_1544620759811.jpg&h=8540f52d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Among the demands, migrants asked the US to accept more asylum applications per day<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/12/12/8632521226266131458/1024x576_MP4_8632521226266131458.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F12%2F12%2F8632521226266131458%2F1024x576_MP4_8632521226266131458.mp4&d=jlMUGUNBB2JG8BQortsepYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d6139da4\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/12/12/8632521226266131458/1024x576_MP4_8632521226266131458.mp4</a><br />\n Migrant caravan marches towards U.S. consulate in Mexico<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/11/29/6030172029888017957/1024x576_MP4_6030172029888017957.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F11%2F29%2F6030172029888017957%2F1024x576_MP4_6030172029888017957.mp4&d=jlMUGUNBB2JG8BQortsepYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=60e56c49\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/11/29/6030172029888017957/1024x576_MP4_6030172029888017957.mp4</a><br />\n Conditions worsen for immigrants in Tijuana on the U.S. border<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6487193/Central-American-migrants-march-consulate-Tijuana-demands-Trump-administration.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-6487193%2FCentral-American-migrants-march-consulate-Tijuana-demands-Trump-administration.html&d=jlMUGUNBB2JG8BQortsepYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2d1494f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6487193/Central-American-migrants-march-consulate-Tijuana-demands-Trump-administration.html</a>"},{"pid":"5cb9b92a8dfcfeed1b00ba1e1fbc90821c720d0b","tid":939291,"uid":109462,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"侵：OK，折算成子彈給付。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21273a96fc1348428e24c81a0cad8be484ae242a","tid":939291,"uid":33645,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"佢地咩理由走黎問人攞錢先.<br />\n我完全唔明"},{"pid":"b28acbf8b04b9dcbb984b2ac9d9ef27df02c0739","tid":939291,"uid":4258,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"21273a96fc1348428e24c81a0cad8be484ae242a","tid":939291,"uid":33645,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"佢地咩理由走黎問人攞錢先.<br />\n我完全唔明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:11:15.000Z","msg":"They also asked the US to remove Honduran President Hernandez from office<br />\n<br />\n我估係cia 發動政變推返當地民選總統啩，不過都好耐之前嘅事。伊朗/中南美友成日嘈依樣。"},{"pid":"faf5c296c72df4adb2d81a5d88bcb6a27d7ff821","tid":939291,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:11:50.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8879f7fcb354bd27171b1f8af7d3569f6634123e","tid":939291,"uid":64191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:16:09.000Z","msg":"$50000 each<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6996f0ec1159af71f10d702b33d98838a074f843","tid":939291,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a189e5220f9702a33f7f56a8b2d19f91b57c32","tid":939291,"uid":51724,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:17:54.000Z","msg":"開槍射佢都唔洗$5美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c398ec8cf6be24c368a7bdfa5bddd180896fc73f","tid":939291,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":43,"score":-40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:19:15.000Z","msg":"從前從前很久以前 大概是三年前<br />\n<br />\n這是一個真實的故事<br />\n<br />\n請大家用很嚴肅的態度 來接受這個故事<br />\n<br />\n我不知道這算不算是一種鬼故事 還是個意寓深遠的勵志話題<br />\n<br />\n總之你他媽既然點進來 就看就對了不要廢話這麼多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從前從前很久以前　大概是三年前<br />\n<br />\n我母親買了一對陶瓷娃娃<br />\n<br />\n那是女兒節要給我姐拿出來擺設用的<br />\n<br />\n我阿嬤的阿嬤的阿嬤客兄　從小就告訴我<br />\n<br />\n當你把陶瓷娃娃收起來的時候<br />\n<br />\n千萬不要把她收在陰暗的角落　或是沒人理會的櫃子裡面<br />\n<br />\n總而言之就是不要不理他　不在乎他<br />\n<br />\n不然家裡一定會發生一些事情<br />\n<br />\n雖然我是個鐵齒不信邪的人<br />\n<br />\n但是總會在朋友耳中聽到一些<br />\n<br />\n什麼娃娃好寂寞　你把他丟了　他還會回到你身邊<br />\n<br />\n又或著是　娃娃躲在櫃子裡頭冷冷清清淡淡今後都不管得哭啼<br />\n<br />\n我也是有點怕怕的<br />\n<br />\n但是時間飛逝　我破了處男了　姐姐也嫁人了　但是因為某些原因<br />\n<br />\n他帶著他的女兒搬回家裡頭住<br />\n<br />\n再過幾天又是女兒節　姪女吵鬧著要對陶瓷娃娃　<br />\n<br />\n看來是對媽媽買的舊陶瓷娃娃不感興趣<br />\n<br />\n當然姐姐也是個愛小孩的人　理所當然去百貨公司買了對陶瓷娃娃　<br />\n<br />\n還隨機附贈十八段變速錄音功能<br />\n<br />\n我姪女這個小王八蛋　立刻就喜新厭舊的把陶瓷娃娃收到櫃子裡頭的最深處　<br />\n<br />\n好似不會再拿出來似的<br />\n<br />\n當天晚上　月亮不是很圓　而隔壁員外那條狗阿福也沒有吹高雷　<br />\n<br />\n我姪女晚上睡覺的時候　一直聽到有人在哭<br />\n<br />\n她很害怕　她抓著我還有我姐姐到處去找那個哭聲<br />\n<br />\n而每當接近那個哭聲一大步　我背脊就越涼一大半<br />\n<br />\n漸漸的　我發現哭聲來自於那個櫃子　而且好似來自於深埋於裏頭的陶瓷娃娃<br />\n<br />\n我們都很害怕　很想把他丟掉　想把他丟到景美溪裡或是銅鑼灣<br />\n<br />\n但又很害怕　娃娃回來報仇<br />\n<br />\n經過我們的討論<br />\n<br />\n我們決定把她上網拍賣掉<br />\n<br />\n一對陶瓷娃娃售價三千元台幣　望有緣人帶走<br />\n<br />\n沒想到這拍賣一登　馬上就有買家標價<br />\n<br />\n當天我就把陶瓷娃娃寄出去<br />\n<br />\n也確認了買家收到這對陶瓷娃娃<br />\n<br />\n過了兩天　又是個狗攬的吹高雷的夜晚<br />\n<br />\n我們一樣睡得很熟　很熟<br />\n<br />\n但三更半夜的時候<br />\n<br />\n我接到一通電話　是一個小女孩<br />\n<br />\n他說他在車站等我　要我趕快去接他<br />\n<br />\n我當然不理他　因為心裡毛毛的<br />\n<br />\n我電話掛掉之後<br />\n<br />\n我們全家人的電話都在同一時間響了起來<br />\n<br />\n全部都是同一個號碼<br />\n<br />\n我姐接了起來<br />\n<br />\n小女孩說　請我們快點去接他　他在車站與小男孩　好冷　好孤單<br />\n<br />\n心裡真的很害怕　但又怕不去車站　萬一她們來找我們　那才真的恐佈<br />\n<br />\n我把我爺爺的八卦鏡帶了出去　跟我姐姐還有姪女到了木柵捷運車站<br />\n<br />\n那時天還沒亮　夜都還是黑的<br />\n<br />\n捷運站門口　我遠遠的看就知道　陶瓷娃娃在門口<br />\n<br />\n我念了大概十次阿彌陀佛　也拜了耶穌玉皇大帝三四次<br />\n<br />\n我憑著　我過人的勇氣　把陶瓷娃娃又帶了回家<br />\n<br />\n這次 我請了隔壁佬王扮成道士來作法<br />\n<br />\n請她們不要再糾纏我們<br />\n<br />\n這次 我一樣用拍賣的方式 以售價三千圓把他標售出去<br />\n<br />\n這次 也順利寄了出去<br />\n<br />\n但是恐怖的事 那天晚上我又接到了同樣的電話<br />\n<br />\n這下我真的不知道該怎麼辦了<br />\n<br />\n我只好鼓起同樣的勇氣 到了車站 又再次把陶瓷娃娃接了回家<br />\n<br />\n但是我心想真的不是辦法<br />\n<br />\n我也沒錢去請真正的道士來作法<br />\n<br />\n我去提款機看看我剩多少錢<br />\n<br />\n　　《餘額 6,000》<br />\n<br />\n我只剩下賣兩次陶瓷娃娃的六千圓<br />\n<br />\n恩和宮裡的道士說要一萬二才肯來作法<br />\n<br />\n在我籌不出錢的急迫下<br />\n<br />\n我只好硬著頭皮　又在把陶瓷娃娃賣出去兩次<br />\n<br />\n這樣一共有一萬二<br />\n<br />\n這時<br />\n<br />\n我突然驚覺<br />\n<br />\n這不是一個賺錢的好方式嗎<br />\n<br />\n之後　我不斷的一直把他用拍賣或是其他的方式把陶瓷娃娃賣掉<br />\n<br />\n反正當天晚上我再去車站接她們就好<br />\n<br />\n久而久之<br />\n<br />\n陶瓷娃娃也會認路了<br />\n<br />\n也會自己走回家<br />\n<br />\n但是她們太矮<br />\n<br />\n還是要我們幫他開門<br />\n<br />\n所以我做了一個小門<br />\n<br />\n而在拍賣的途中　我也試著讓她們看著　如何使用拍賣<br />\n<br />\n最後她們也會自己在我們睡著的時候　利用電腦把自己拍賣出去<br />\n<br />\n經過這樣的反覆<br />\n<br />\n三千圓三千圓這樣子的積沙成塔<br />\n<br />\n我也存到了人生的第一棟房子<br />\n<br />\n我也開始不愁吃穿<br />\n<br />\n直到最近　我發現台灣百大富豪　我居然也名列於此<br />\n<br />\n這真的是不可思議<br />\n<br />\n這是個嚴肅的故事<br />\n<br />\n請大家好好想想故事裡頭　是要告訴你什麼<br />\n<br />\n你要知道　每當你提起陶瓷娃娃的時候<br />\n<br />\n陶瓷娃娃就會在某個角落注視著你<br />\n<br />\n所以不要隨便提起他<br />\n<br />\n我希望這個故事能夠到我這邊就結束了<br />\n<br />\nＥＮＤ"},{"pid":"e19875fca567286d267aa20b1fde571e84f51fd4","tid":939291,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T05:08:43.000Z","msg":"用50000換曬做1蚊美金<br />\n係聚集地度灑出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時自然解決問題"},{"pid":"3a33003752517b4a0e3e5ca80c949cb515afa0ce","tid":939291,"uid":134215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5cb9b92a8dfcfeed1b00ba1e1fbc90821c720d0b","tid":939291,"uid":109462,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"侵：OK，折算成子彈給付。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T05:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/486685319015669384/E5C5D7F75588E1801201772DBAC2B4C25BE89DC1/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net%2Fugc%2F486685319015669384%2FE5C5D7F75588E1801201772DBAC2B4C25BE89DC1%2F&h=055804eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到呢句就諗起TF2個heavy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIt costs <span style=\"color: red;\">400,000 dollars</span> to fire this weapon... for 12 seconds.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國咁撚有錢 係我就唔忍啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1a5ee33cdbb232aa94c7b65bd6c91b2bd7c199","tid":939291,"uid":31017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"冇須審判，立刻槍斃<br />\n收取子彈消耗費0.5美元<br />\n對付呢d「難民」<br />\n土匪辨法有效好多"},{"pid":"4a06e653dfed03480325ef8fb82be75ce5e905de","tid":939291,"uid":62409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"叫何里活啲明星俾啦<br />\n成日post文話呢話路"},{"pid":"79365e44b2eee09d8962634dad7a6085ae48597e","tid":939291,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa1a5ee33cdbb232aa94c7b65bd6c91b2bd7c199","tid":939291,"uid":31017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"冇須審判，立刻槍斃<br />\n收取子彈消耗費0.5美元<br />\n對付呢d「難民」<br />\n土匪辨法有效好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T06:00:06.000Z","msg":"人地要錢做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7918b5ee908f04e696f95b28f2279e807c6755","tid":939291,"uid":71596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T06:02:26.000Z","msg":"開槍 啦<br />\n入侵人地國家仲問人拎錢<br />\n同支蛆一撚樣"},{"pid":"f8bb2aebd106354ade88ec57d5e41af60384c776","tid":939291,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cade8c4477a931ec6c0128346b37833c0acb1bc0","tid":939291,"uid":66119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"洗哂再偷渡過黎 <img src=\"/asset